Module com.example.projectthree
Package com.example.Projv3

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
com.example.Projv3.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
This is the Fitness Class for all the fitness classes to check in or drop. This class is mainly for tracking which members have been added to the current class choosing from Pilates, Spinning and Cardio. This class accesses the MemberDatabase class to see if they are registered into any class and if so which class. This class also has to functionality of printing schedules of classes.
Author:
Abhijeet Singh, Khizar Saud

    • checkIn

      public boolean checkIn(Member member, MemberDatabase memberDb, String className, FitnessClass Fitness)
      This class is for checking a member into a class if they haven't checked in already. This method takes care of if the member is enrolled already. This method also takes care of if the member exists. This method also takes care of if the memeber's membership has expired or not. If they pass the conditions they will be checked into the class
      Parameters:
      member - the memeber that needs to be checked in
      memberDb - For checking if the member is in the database.
      className - The name of the class member is checking into.
